{"tid":464004,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬建議出售卡雲尼 籌錢買一人","createTime":"2017-11-10T05:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T15:46:59.000Z","uid":59732,"like":62,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"f65c1a8413ecfb5544f31974bbb0538f32e71027","tid":464004,"uid":59732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2017/11/10/d/d0abbb44c77d26bd2ee352d791954125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2Fd%2Fd0abbb44c77d26bd2ee352d791954125.jpg&h=93c54ae9&s={SIZE}\" />最近一段時間，法國媒體連續報導尼馬在巴黎聖日耳門的一些負面新聞，而據法國媒體《le10sport》報導，尼馬建議巴黎聖日耳門從利物浦購買他的巴西同胞古天奴，但同時他建議球會出售卡雲尼，以保證財政平衡。<br />\n<br />\n　　之前《le10sport》就報導過尼馬向巴黎推薦古天奴，如今他們進行了後續報導，據悉利物浦給古天奴標價8000萬-1億歐元，由於財政公平政策的存在，巴黎需要出售球員，想要得到古天奴，巴黎需要至少完成兩筆大的賣人。<br />\n<br />\n　　根據《le10sport》得到的最新消息，尼馬已經發消息提出建議，讓巴黎在明年夏天賣掉卡雲尼，為買入古天奴提供資金。尼馬希望巴黎能加快買入古天奴的速度。"},{"pid":"4da85c6762d17e57bb12d5931b75e98d3a0c1f48","tid":464004,"uid":52571,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:43:49.000Z","msg":"Benzema係最完美代替品"},{"pid":"c55b581ee11dbfc5134425c0669949b7a4ebca18","tid":464004,"uid":12252,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:46:04.000Z","msg":"成隊巴西國家隊"},{"pid":"2e9835b3d32f49075fd0c26f75fe1ef7e560364c","tid":464004,"uid":9164,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:46:14.000Z","msg":"賣撚咗痢螞咪買到古天奴返黎囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d14820d944c60b0c6c469193c58eba7ae79aab","tid":464004,"uid":19552,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:46:44.000Z","msg":"巴塞甩左件麻煩友"},{"pid":"24b484e08021bd4149500b2087bcb2f8638f79e2","tid":464004,"uid":20522,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Benzema係最完美代替品</blockquote><br />\n拉空畀尼馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\